*gammu-1.04.0-r2 (08 Jan 2006)

  08 Jan 2006; Alin Nastac <mrness@gentoo.org> -gammu-1.04.0-r1.ebuild,
  +gammu-1.04.0-r2.ebuild:
  Add installation of the shared library (#118074).

*gammu-1.04.0-r1 (07 Jan 2006)

  07 Jan 2006; Alin Nastac <mrness@gentoo.org>
  +files/gammu-1.04.0-devfunc-sock.patch, -gammu-1.04.0.ebuild,
  +gammu-1.04.0-r1.ebuild:
  Ebuild redesign imposed by upstream changes (#118074). The new ebuild don\t
  add --enable-6210calendar to configure line since it forces gammu to use
  Nokia 6210 frames for calendar, frames that are incompatible with other
  models (#117350).

  02 Jan 2006; Michael Hanselmann <hansmi@gentoo.org> gammu-1.02.0.ebuild:
  Stable on ppc.

*gammu-1.04.0 (02 Jan 2006)

